{"tid":1509930,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]黑警濫權罪狀表","createTime":"2019-08-27T04:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T04:26:00.000Z","uid":89774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c04d3eab944b2cca9594ac3325664a7f3b7c8a2e","tid":1509930,"uid":89774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"唔批不反對通知書，市民遊行超過時間-&gt;非法集結<br />\n黑警使用過高武力，市民合理自衞-&gt;襲警<br />\n街坊落樓下散步-&gt;非法集結<br />\n行得慢-&gt;阻差辦公<br />\n比黑社會打-&gt;公眾地方行為不檢<br />\n比人拉入狗屋女女女，比抗-&gt;又點搵藉口?屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多<br />\n<br />\n無理由次次黑警濫權都可以比政府合理化，點點次次都比佢地譴責，我地冇得譴責?<br />\n<br />\n點解次次黑警可以合理化打尻我地，我地仲要係暴徒? 邊撚個先係暴徒?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，分開戰線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以整一個由612到而家既文宣，講黑警點樣濫權，開頭可以愈簡略愈好，有唔同語言，等外國可以更易知黑警仆街行為</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n好撚嬲，唔可以比前線勇武巴打咁孤單<br />\n<br />\n後面和理非都要文宣幫手!!!!!"},{"pid":"af932c7ecd8ef27070d31853e7083e486ea2f49a","tid":1509930,"uid":89774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:03:13.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"12c6d8fffa1ab354db8e263005631d81a596f35e","tid":1509930,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQro26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=d0fcff03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQro26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=b9fcaaaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"h